Package com.interzoid.sdk.model

Class InterzoidResponse

java.lang.Object
com.interzoid.sdk.model.InterzoidResponse
Direct Known Subclasses:
MatchKeyResponse, MatchScoreResponse
public class InterzoidResponse extends Object
Represents the response structure for Interzoid API responses. This class contains fields to store the API response code and available credits.
